YAML-Accessor version 0.10
==========================

I saw a need to integrate Class::Accessor with YAML::XS. You
may not see this need, but I wanted it and I use it for a piece
of code that sorely needs it. Here you go. Use it or don't.

XXX: THIS IS PRE-BETA SOFTWARE.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  YAML::XS
  Class::Accessor
  Params::Validate

